---
import "@fontsource-variable/source-code-pro";
import '@fontsource/fira-sans/100.css';
import '@fontsource/fira-sans/200.css';
import '@fontsource/fira-sans/300.css';
import '@fontsource/fira-sans/400.css';
import '@fontsource/fira-sans/500.css';
import '@fontsource/fira-sans/600.css';
import '@fontsource/fira-sans/700.css';
import '@fontsource/fira-sans/800.css';
import '@fontsource/fira-sans/900.css';import "@fontsource/rubik-mono-one";
import Header from "../components/Header";
import Footer from "../components/Footer";
// 1. The frontmatter prop gives access to frontmatter and other data
const { frontmatter } = Astro.props;
---

<html>
  <head>
    <title>{frontmatter.title} | Jared Asuncion</title>
    <!-- Add other Head elements here, like styles and meta tags. -->
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="title" content={`${frontmatter.title} | Jared Asuncion`} />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content={`${frontmatter.description} | Jared Asuncion`}
    />
    <meta name="author" content="Jared Asuncion" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      type="text/css"
      href=`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/style.css`
    />
    <link rel="sitemap" href=`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/sitemap-index.xml` />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.15.2/dist/katex.min.css"
      integrity="sha384-MlJdn/WNKDGXveldHDdyRP1R4CTHr3FeuDNfhsLPYrq2t0UBkUdK2jyTnXPEK1NQ"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link
      rel="apple-touch-icon"
      sizes="180x180"
      href="/blog/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png"
    />
    <link
      rel="icon"
      type="image/png"
      sizes="32x32"
      href="/blog/favicon/favicon-32x32.png"
    />
    <link
      rel="icon"
      type="image/png"
      sizes="16x16"
      href="/blog/favicon/favicon-16x16.png"
    />
    <link rel="manifest" href="/blog/favicon/site.webmanifest" />
    <title>{frontmatter.title}</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <Header />
      <div class="breadcrumbs">
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`}>Home</a>
        <span class="raquo">&raquo;</span>
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/blog`}>Blog</a>
        <span class="raquo">&raquo;</span>
        <a href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/blog/category/${frontmatter.category.toLowerCase().replaceAll(" ","-")}`}>{frontmatter.category}</a>
        <span class="raquo">&raquo;</span>
        <a href="#">{frontmatter.title}</a>
      </div>
      <!-- Add other UI components here, like common headers and footers. -->
      <h1>{frontmatter.title}</h1>
      <!-- 2. Rendered HTML will be passed into the default slot. -->
      <span class="content">
        <div class="preface">
          Il s'agit d'une collaboration entre moi, <b>Jared Asuncion</b>, et le prof de maths <b>Pierre Brun</b> pour r√©aliser ces notes de cours.
          Ce sont les notes de cours pour son cours d'NSI en terminale pendant l'ann√©e acad√©mique 2024-2025.
          Elles ont √©t√© initialement r√©dig√©es sous forme de notebooks Jupyter, mais nous les avons converties en HTML pour une meilleure lisibilit√© dans les browsers.
          <p>C'est un travail en cours. N'h√©sitez pas √† nous contacter √† <a href="mailto:nsi@guissmo.com">nsi@guissmo.com</a> pour vos commentaires, suggestions, encouragements ou offres de pr√©pa (pour Pierre) !</p>
        </div>
        <slot />
      </span>
      <Footer />
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style is:global>
  body {
    font-family: "Fira Sans", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  h1:not(#logo) {
    font-weight: 800;
    padding-top: 2ex;
  }

  .content {
    padding-top: 3ex;
  }

  p code,
  li code {
    font-family: "Source Code Pro Variable", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    border: 1px solid darkgray;
    border-radius: 5px;
    padding-left: 0.3em;
    padding-right: 0.3em;
  }

div.rendered_html {
	font-family: "";
	color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8)!important;
}

h2 {
	color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1);
}

h3 {
	color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
	text-decoration: underline;
}

h4 {
	color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
}

div.test {
	color: red;
	border: 1px solid black;
}
div.info {
	margin-top: 3px;
	margin-bottom: 3px;
	padding: 12px;
	background: aliceblue;
	border-left: 3px solid skyblue;
}
div.warn {
	margin-top: 3px;
	margin-bottom: 3px;
	padding: 12px;
	background: lightyellow;
	border-left: 3px solid goldenrod;
}
div.err {
	margin-top: 3px;
	margin-bottom: 3px;
	padding: 12px;
	background: lightpink;
	border-left: 3px solid darkred;
}
div.example {
	margin-top: 3px;
	margin-bottom: 3px;
	padding: 12px;
	background: #e2fee2;
	border-left: 3px solid teal;
}
div.exer-start::before {
	content: 'EXERCICE';
	font-weight: bold;
	text-align: center;
}
div.exer-start-live::before {
	content: 'EXERCICE TOUS ENSEMBLE';
	font-weight: bold;
	text-align: center;
}
div.exer-hard::before {
	content: 'EXERCICE ‚≠ê'
}
div.exer-champ::before {
	content: 'EXERCICE 'üèÜ
}
div.text_cell_render {
	overflow-y: visible;
}
div.rendered_html li {
	padding-top: 1ex;
	padding-bottom: 1ex;
}
div.exer-start, div.exer-start-live {
	transform: translateY(24px);
	margin-left: 24px;
	margin-right: 24px;
	padding: 24px;
	border: 2px dashed #cfcfcf;
	background: #fcfcfc;
	border-bottom-style: none;
}
div.exer-mid {
	margin-left: 24px;
	margin-right: 24px;
	padding: 24px;
	margin-bottom: 0;
	border: 2px dashed #cfcfcf;
	background: #fcfcfc;
	border-bottom-style: none;
	border-top-style: none;
}
div.exer-end {
	transform: translateY(-24px);
	margin-left: 24px;
	margin-right: 24px;
	padding: 24px;
	border: 2px dashed #cfcfcf;
	background: #fcfcfc;
	border-top-style: none;
}
div.exer-live {
	background: #e2fee2;
	border-color: teal;
}

code {
	font-family: "Source Code Pro", "DejaVu Sans Mono", monospace;
}

.CodeMirror {
	font-family: "Source Code Pro", "DejaVu Sans Mono", monospace;
	padding: 10px;
}
div.cm-s-ipython, div.text_cell_render pre {
	font-size: 1em;
	line-height: 1.5em;
	letter-spacing: 0.3px;
	word-spacing: 1px;
	background: #1B2630!important;
	color: #F8F8F2!important;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.CodeMirror-lines {
	padding: 8px 0;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.CodeMirror-gutters {
	box-shadow: 1px 0 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	-webkit-box-shadow: 1px 0 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	background-color: #1B2630;
	padding-right: 10px;
	z-index: 3;
	border: none;
}
.cm-s-ipython div.CodeMirror-cursor {
	border-left: 3px solid #F8F8F2;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.CodeMirror-activeline-background {
	background: #3D2E2E77;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.CodeMirror-selected {
	background: #95A3A63D;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.cm-comment {
	font-style: unset!important;
	color: #6D6D6D;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.cm-string {
	color: #8AD6F2;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.cm-number {
	color: #FFB266;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.cm-atom {
	color: #FFB266;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.cm-keyword {
	color: #E47D80;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.cm-variable {
	color: #F2AAEC;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.cm-def {
/*	font-style: italic;*/
	color: #FFD2A6;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.cm-variable-2, .cm-s-ipython span.cm-builtin {
	color: #BAE682;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.cm-property {
	color: #FFB266;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.cm-operator {
	color: #E47D80;
}
.cm-s-ipython span.CodeMirror-linenumber {
	color: #6D6D6D;
}
div.output_subarea {
	background-color: #f1f1f1;
	align-self: center;
	max-width: 100%;
}
div.prompt_container, div.prompt {
	display: none;
}

div.exer-start, div.exer-mid, div.exer-end {
  position: relative;
  z-index: -1;
}

div.info, div.warn, div.err, div.example {
  margin-top: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

div.preface {
  border: 2px dotted green;
  border-left-width: 0;
  border-right-width: 0;
  padding-top: 12px;
  color: green;
  line-height: 1.5;
  padding-left: 1em;
}
</style>
